B.PZ=new A.Z("The crew was forced to divert to Valencia after a hydraulic failure.","Ekip, hidrolik ar\u0131zas\u0131n\u0131n ard\u0131ndan Valencia'ya y\xf6n de\u011fi\u015ftirmek zorunda kald\u0131.","divert")
