B.XR=new A.m(B.an,"\u2708\ufe0f S\u0131nav \u0130pucu","S\u0131navda s\u0131k kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lan \xe7iftler:\n\u2022 **IAS** (G\xf6sterge Hava H\u0131z\u0131) vs. **TAS** (Ger\xe7ek Hava H\u0131z\u0131) \u2014 TAS irtifayla artar\n\u2022 **FMS** t\xfcm rotay\u0131 y\xf6netir | **otopilot** u\xe7a\u011f\u0131 kontrol eder\n\u2022 **TCAS RA** = zorunlu ka\xe7\u0131nma manevras\u0131 | **TCAS TA** = Trafik Tavsiyesi (yaln\u0131zca fark\u0131ndal\u0131k)\n\u2022 **DME** **e\u011fim mesafesini** \xf6l\xe7er (yer mesafesi de\u011fil)\n\u2022 **IRS** ba\u011f\u0131ms\u0131zd\u0131r (d\u0131\u015f sinyal gerekmez) | **GPS** uydular\u0131 gerektirir",null,null,null)
