B.a_1=new A.m(B.v,"\u0130leri Yap\u0131lar",'**Perfect Passive:**\n\u2022 has/have been + V3 \u2192 "The engine has been inspected."\n\u2022 had been + V3 \u2192 "The part had been replaced before the flight."\n\n**Future Passive:**\n\u2022 will be + V3 \u2192 "The aircraft will be returned to service."\n\u2022 is going to be + V3 \u2192 "The runway is going to be closed."\n\n**Causative:**\n\u2022 have + object + V3 \u2192 "The airline had the engine overhauled."\n\u2022 get + object + V3 \u2192 "The crew got the fault rectified."\n\n**Reporting Passive:**\n\u2022 It is reported that\u2026 / It is believed that\u2026\n\u2022 The aircraft is reported to have deviated from the assigned route.',null,null,null)
